name: Gem404
description: The first ERC-404 on Avalanche. Purchase 1 $GEM and automatically a GEM NFT appears in your wallet that can be sold on OKX, OpenSea and JoePegs. That is the beauty of 404s. Based on the Chinese tradition of GEM gambling, the team will be announcing various stages of a Game, where users will have to collect tools to open the GEM and reveal the hidden image.
